verbose_text: In a group of 63 non obese CHC patients (29 M/34 F) infected with genotype 1b aged 46.6 +/-14.6 years, body mass index (BMI) 24.8 +/-3.0 kg/m 2, serum visfatin levels and its mRNA hepatic expression were examined and the subsequent associations with metabolic and histopathological features were assessed.
